{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"df5e815a07","title":"无政府主义和社会主义","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c524a9e5e6","index":0,"year":1901,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"df5e815a07"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","name":"列宁选集 第一卷（1972年）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"列宁，人民出版社1972年","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"b353e6fb43","name":"列宁"}]},"publication_details":{"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a63bd2494e","type":"paragraph","text":"无政府主义和社会主义提纲。","index":0,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"38bc4b8d8b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）无政府主义在产生以来的三十五至四十年中（从巴枯宁和1866年国际代表大会算起是这样。从施蒂纳算起，那还要早很多年）除了讲一些反对购削的空话以外，再没有提供任何东西。","index":1,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"0937fa5d38","type":"paragraph","text":"这种空话已经流行两千多年了。（a）不懂得剥削的根源：（8）不懂得社会在向社会主义发展；（）不懂得阶级斗争是实现社会主义的创造力量。","index":2,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"d83ae83ff4","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）对于剥削的根源的了解。私有制是商品经济的基础。生产资料公有制。无政府主义对这些一跨不通。","index":3,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"d35dfb1dba","type":"paragraph","text":"无政府主义是改头换面的资产阶级个人主义。个人主义是无政府主义整个世界观的基础。","index":4,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"7bfb77904d","type":"paragraph","text":"维护小私有制和土地上的小农经济。Keine Majoritat.否认政权有统一的和组织的力量。","index":5,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"5059e273e1","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）不懂得社会的发展———大生产的作用-一从资本主义向社会主义的发展。","index":6,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"8374ceff26","type":"paragraph","text":"（无政府主义是绝望的产物。它是失常的知识分子或游民的心理状态，而不是无产者的心理状态。①无所调多数（也就是无政府主义者否认少数服从多数）。编着注（4）不懂得无产阶级的阶级斗争。荒地否认资产阶级社会的政治。不懂得组织和教育工人的作用。把片面的、割断了联系的手段当作方应灵丹。","index":7,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"457ec00040","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）在欧洲的现代史中，曾经在罗曼语各国流行一时的无政府主义，提供了什么东西呢","index":8,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"007c3906ed","type":"paragraph","text":"一没有任何学理、任何革命学说和革命理论。一分散工人运动。","index":9,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"930ff29c1e","type":"paragraph","text":"一在革命运动的实验中彻底破产（1871年的蒲鲁东主义117，1873年的巴枯宁主义136）。","index":10,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"f3c8c1b906","type":"paragraph","text":"一在否定政治的子下使工人阶级服从资产阶级的政治。","index":11,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"704efe6a45","type":"paragraph","text":"按手稿刊印写于1901年","index":12,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"11668954c2","type":"paragraph","text":"选自《列宁全集第5卷第一次载于1936年","index":13,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"},{"id":"f235b382a3","type":"paragraph","text":"第294-297页《无产阶级革命》杂志第7期","index":14,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07"}],"page":{"id":"2e22698851","publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"df5e815a07","start":230,"end":231}}}},"__N_SSG":true}